ormal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你仲有咩唔舒服？<br />\n不過你一日未夠嚴重，<br />\n西醫都係話你咩氣管敏感開止咳藥比你算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本來喉嚨發炎，而家只係不停咳咳咳，失哂聲咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248844a3faedc3b31325c20d76309e838e8540d0","tid":496591,"uid":64767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:01:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痰是否淡色？早晚咳係涼咳，睇中醫。其他病唔敢講，咳真係睇中醫最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 啱啱咳完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係淡，其實冇咩痰，係唔知點解瘋狂咳，睇左，飲左一劑好似冇咩用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c32bf38776c29e2956281bc70b9d441143cbcd8","tid":496591,"uid":64767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:01:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乾咳定有痰嗰啲？<br />\n之前試過乾咳咗好耐 醫生話支氣管炎 打咗支針 第二日就無事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乾咳呀，睇左六七次醫生都冇個醫生咁講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aafc72c584ed1d0666820b1520449d619ac2198","tid":496591,"uid":64767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:02:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>日頭都ok，一到夜晚就咳撚到仆街，明明無咩鼻水但一吸氣就搞到個喉嚨好撚痕，每一下吸氣都咳，係每一下呀屌，成兩星期無訓過好覺啦on99，求救 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真答：跑步，唔駛多，一日20-30分鐘，試三幾日，好就繼續，唔好就當我鳩up。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry仲有，可以多食洋蔥，訓覺用圍巾或者衫圍住頸項唔好比風吹，呢個幾work。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n病好左先跑步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b3d914aa32ee0276758ed312835dd39335fcc8","tid":496591,"uid":64767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:02:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主買定棺材啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買定俾你呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42af810e18cf389286fab08cc9f2