,"uid":45817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T11:10:01.000Z","msg":"屌，我係感冒完就咳左成個星期"},{"pid":"a1ef70a21f5ffb0663be8b71e67f11ecbb7408a0","tid":496591,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T11:22:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可能氣管敏感<br />\n<br />\n我上年冬天又係感冒完之後咳到停唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚咳到覺都瞓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇咗十次西醫睇埋專科都好唔到 一停藥又再咳過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後係太子睇咗個好勁嘅中醫飲咗一劑藥就停咗咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話我係鼻炎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇十次銀包真係好撚痛 <br />\n邊個中醫，唔理你係咪打手，開名呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你search韓兼思<br />\n佢收得唔貴，我覺得平過其他中醫<br />\n我個時睇過浸會醫院中醫都唔得<br />\n西醫專科連街症都睇埋都搞唔掂<br />\n已經係絕望到諗住咩都試下<br />\n點知一飲就停左咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過可能中醫都人夾人<br />\n你可以試下執兩三包藥睇下有冇用先<br />\n希望幫到你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我都明咳足成個月都唔停覺又瞓唔到第二朝仲要返工有幾灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過佢唔係日日開<br />\n同埋要拎籌<br />\n都幾多人睇，放工去都要等一個鐘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪冇得打電話去預約？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以我所知冇<br />\n但佢淨係開一三五六 10:30am-1pm 4:30pm-7pm<br />\n如果你返工前或者lunch去唔到拎籌就要放工去等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e777be9577f72338a7e2351244f7f923f75180","tid":496591,"uid":19278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T11:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可能<span style=\"color: red;\">氣管敏感</span><br />\n<br />\n我上年冬天又係感冒完之後咳到停唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚咳到覺都瞓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇咗十次西醫睇埋專科都好唔到 一停藥又再咳過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後係太子睇咗個好勁嘅中醫飲咗一劑藥就停咗咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話我係<span style=\"color: red;\">鼻炎</span></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以分享下係邊個中醫?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以上既事都係腎差引致<br />\n得閒補下</blockquote><br />\n可以點補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應該都幾真係差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個中醫幫我把脈左手弱到聽唔到 要把右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ead4670911c3c437f6aeacef23b8229deb56a1","tid":496591,"uid":55391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:56:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可能<span style=\"color: red;\">氣管敏感</span><br />\n<br />\n我上年冬天又係感冒完之後咳到停唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚咳到覺都瞓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇咗十次西醫睇埋專科都好唔到 一停藥又再咳過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後係太子睇咗個好勁嘅中醫飲咗一劑藥就停咗咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話我係<span style=\"color: red;\">鼻炎</span></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以分享下係邊個中醫?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以上既事都係腎差引致<br />\n得閒補下</blockquote><br />\n可以點補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應該都幾真係差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個中醫幫我把脈左手弱到聽唔到 要把右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戒丁"},{"pid":"48d785532f9046f7f515f6b7ae8f0b04fedb961f","tid":496591,"uid":64767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T01:33:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可能氣管敏感<br />\n<br />\n我上年冬天又係感冒完之後咳到停唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚咳到覺都瞓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇咗十次西醫睇埋專科都好唔到 一停藥又再咳過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後係太子睇咗個好勁嘅中醫飲咗一劑藥就停咗咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話我係鼻炎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇十次銀包真係好撚痛 <br />\n邊個中醫，唔理你係咪打手，開名呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你search韓兼思<br />\n佢收得唔貴，我覺得平過其他中醫<br />\n我個時睇過浸會醫院中醫都唔得<br />\n西醫專科連街症都睇埋都搞唔掂<br />\n已經係絕望到諗住咩都試下<br />\n點知一飲就停左咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過可能中醫都人夾人<br />\n你可以試下執兩三包藥睇下有冇用先<br />\n希望幫到你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我都明咳足成個月都唔停覺又瞓唔到第二朝仲要返工有幾灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打，呢兩日咳少左，不過仲未清得哂，<br />\n同埋咳到背隻肌肉同坐骨神經痛，今次真係大撚獲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d188074c736d41c3acf8f781b63abb47dd9a39","tid":496591,"uid":127269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T01:40:50.000Z","msg":"薑加陳皮滾水,唔使煲好耐,用保暖壺KEEP住,咳就飲一兩啖"},{"pid":"6100fcdcf9fce5cf4d3e3168791fdcd2cec63ea5","tid":496591,"uid":80055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T01:48:53.000Z","msg":"應該係氣管敏感<br />\n睇中醫同多做運動 個人覺得西醫幫唔到咩手<br />\n跑多d步 最好就係多d去行山 但唔好行得太慢 最好keep住喘氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跑步每次都要跑耐d 唔好跑廿分鐘就停<br />\n中醫樓上巴打提果個中醫我都試下 係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 多次氣管敏感經歷🤦&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"97ed340015f600208174cc06b2a96a07c5de8ae8","tid":496591,"uid":10951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T02:07:09.000Z","msg":"每逢轉天氣<br />\n我老母好鍾意沖<br />\n金銀花，白菊花，蜜冬，花旗参，再加少少鹽<br />\n好多時飲完就少咳好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9650afad3aac4f78ec358da663c618bce3a1cd96","tid":496591,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:59:53.000Z","msg":"去照肺啦 咳咁耐都唔好有可能cancer"},{"pid":"5966f678e7672d95da16fe1b158b3766d4bc3a3e","tid":496591,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:45:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可能<span style=\"color: red;\">氣管敏感</span><br />\n<br />\n我上年冬天又係感冒完之後咳到停唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚咳到覺都瞓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇咗十次西醫睇埋專科都好唔到 一停藥又再咳過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後係太子睇咗個好勁嘅中醫飲咗一劑藥就停咗咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話我係<span style=\"color: red;\">鼻炎</span></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以分享下係邊個中醫?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以上既事都係腎差引致<br />\n得閒補下</blockquote><br />\n可以點補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應該都幾真係差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個中醫幫我把脈左手弱到聽唔到 要把右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戒丁</blockquote><br />\n我係絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a549a57b8b8512dfd046b89c1ebf9329245b9c","tid":496591,"uid":64767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:17:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去照肺啦 咳咁耐都唔好有可能cancer</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇留言見到好多咳成個幾兩個月都未好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發現兩星期算好小事"},{"pid":"1da0dbb2e7ad430a9ac1e991ac86a6b3075b26df","tid":496591,"uid":56907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:05:58.000Z","msg":"我又係咳咗成個月先好得返，條氣管好似比人掐住咁收縮。初頭係扁桃腺發炎，跟住變埋支氣管炎<br />\n咳到要食安眠藥先有得瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去邊都要keep住戴口罩，係屋企都要戴。<br />\n水果凍飲甜野煙酒基本上唔駛諗，咳到喉嚨勁痛就食流質食物。<br />\n睇西醫都係舒緩止咳，停咗咳就要補充返抵抗力，可以試下飲維多C同做運動，唔好大聲講野同埋要睇中醫調理。<br />\n<br />\n利申：啱啱好返"},{"pid":"5f505d48c3b0a995b48a5bd42735193988797fcf","tid":496591,"uid":49695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:17:03.000Z","msg":"咳左兩個月喇"},{"pid":"17b65da63e4a6235672b798aae06a09ca9490809","tid":496591,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T17:52:58.000Z","msg":"做咩叫人睇中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c425f0d873d202ee40056c31a403787984d17f7","tid":496591,"uid":105462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T18:03:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日頭都ok，一到夜晚就咳撚到仆街，明明無咩鼻水但一吸氣就搞到個喉嚨好撚痕，每一下吸氣都咳，係每一下呀屌，成兩星期無訓過好覺啦on99，求救 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n氣管敏感  同你情況相若  <br />\n咳到肌肉痛頂唔順去左睇醫生"},{"pid":"092cc79dbe2a1df0c25a42b7e6390fa8a911b459","tid":496591,"uid":66499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:08:22.000Z","msg":"我細細個就 有狂咳嘅情況 <br />\n日頭好啲 正常人地傷風感冒咁<br />\n但夜晚就狂咳 咳到抖唔到氣咁 <br />\n跟手睇醫生 我睇中醫 佢就話我係寒咳<br />\n叫我有痰就吐出嚟<br />\n西醫就話我係哮喘<br />\n<br />\n跟住唔記邊阿叔個同我屋企人講 <br />\n叫我用晚晚熱水袋放係背脊到 瞓教 <br />\n我個情況就好好多<br />\n<br />\n真係好多謝個阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458d74af92851197bc6056335506b902fc73396a","tid":496591,"uid":66499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我細細個就 有狂咳嘅情況 <br />\n日頭好啲 正常人地傷風感冒咁<br />\n但夜晚就狂咳 咳到抖唔到氣咁 <br />\n跟手睇醫生 我睇中醫 佢就話我係寒咳<br />\n叫我有痰就吐出嚟<br />\n西醫就話我係哮喘<br />\n<br />\n跟住唔記邊阿叔個同我屋企人講 <br />\n叫我用晚晚熱水袋放係背脊到 瞓教 <br />\n我個情況就好好多<br />\n<br />\n真係好多謝個阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我見樓主你個情況同我差唔多 <br />\n<br />\n我一發病係 日頭冇咩事 <br />\n一夜晚就泥料 <br />\n喉嚨痕 狂咳 吐白痰 啲痰係有啲泡泡<br />\n另外我係煲陳皮加薑水<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你"},{"pid":"72fe992232dee255b264293487bf4ac0aad226b1","tid":496591,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:49:44.000Z","msg":"LM"}]}